<div class="content page pt-4">
    <p>Welcome to my digital garden or "second brain", a collection of notes maintained using the Personal Knowledge Management system <a href="/notes/r.tech.software.dendron/">Dendron</a>.</p>

    <p>Most of these pages are links or snippets I have copy-pasted or written for my own use, but maybe something here is useful for others too.</p>
